sequenceDiagram
    participant Consumer as Consuming Service<br/>(KFP / CLI / Notebook)
    participant Exp as AI4RAGExperiment
    participant MPS as ModelsPreSelector
    participant SS as SearchSpace
    participant GAM as GAMOptimizer
    participant Chunker as Chunker<br/>(LangChain / Docling)
    participant Eval as UnitxtEvaluator
    participant OGX as OGX Server<br/>HTTPS / TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key Auth
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB<br/>(in-memory)

    Note over Consumer,Chroma: Flow 1: RAG Optimization Experiment

    Consumer->>Exp: start experiment<br/>(template, search_space, benchmark)
    Exp->>SS: prepare_search_space_with_ogx()
    SS->>OGX: GET models.list<br/>HTTPS / API Key
    OGX-->>SS: available models
    SS->>SS: apply 7 constraint rules<br/>(prune invalid combos)

    Note over Exp,Chroma: Models Pre-Selection (MPS) Phase

    alt >3 foundation models or >2 embedding models
        Exp->>MPS: pre-select models<br/>(5 sample questions)
        loop For each model pair
            MPS->>OGX: POST embeddings.create<br/>HTTPS / API Key
            OGX-->>MPS: embeddings
            MPS->>Chroma: store chunks (in-memory)
            MPS->>OGX: POST vector_io.query<br/>HTTPS / API Key
            OGX-->>MPS: retrieval results
            MPS->>OGX: POST chat.completions<br/>HTTPS / API Key
            OGX-->>MPS: generated answer
            MPS->>Eval: evaluate (unitxt)
            Eval-->>MPS: score
        end
        MPS-->>Exp: top foundation + embedding models
    end

    Note over Exp,Chroma: HPO Optimization Phase

    Exp->>GAM: initialize optimizer<br/>(search space, known observations)

    loop For each iteration
        GAM->>GAM: predict best params<br/>(GAM model after n_random=4)
        GAM->>Exp: next parameter combination

        Note over Exp,OGX: Single RAG Pattern Evaluation
        Exp->>Chunker: chunk documents<br/>(in-process)
        Chunker-->>Exp: chunks (with SHA-256 dedup)

        alt Collection not reused
            Exp->>OGX: POST vector_stores.create<br/>HTTPS / API Key
            OGX-->>Exp: collection created
            Exp->>OGX: POST embeddings.create + vector_io.insert<br/>HTTPS / API Key
            OGX-->>Exp: chunks indexed
        else Same indexing params (reuse collection)
            Note over Exp,OGX: Skip re-indexing (collection reuse optimization)
        end

        Exp->>OGX: POST vector_io.query<br/>HTTPS / API Key
        OGX-->>Exp: retrieved context chunks
        Exp->>OGX: POST chat.completions<br/>HTTPS / API Key
        OGX-->>Exp: generated answer
        Exp->>Eval: evaluate<br/>(answer_correctness,<br/>faithfulness,<br/>context_correctness)
        Eval-->>Exp: aggregated score
        Exp->>GAM: report score
        Exp->>Consumer: event: pattern evaluated<br/>(via EventHandler)
    end

    GAM-->>Exp: best parameters found
    Exp-->>Consumer: ExperimentResults<br/>(best pattern, all evaluations)

    Note over Consumer,Chroma: Flow 2: Post-Optimization Inference

    Consumer->>Exp: SimpleRAG.generate(query)
    Exp->>OGX: POST vector_io.query<br/>HTTPS / API Key
    OGX-->>Exp: relevant chunks
    Exp->>OGX: POST chat.completions<br/>HTTPS / API Key
    OGX-->>Exp: generated answer
    Exp-->>Consumer: answer + context
